channel.title: Default Gateway, Router page error--Help Please
channel.description:
When I open Internet Explorer/Firefox and type in my Default Gateway in the URL box to get to my router setup page i get this: For IE: "Internet Explorer cannot display the webpage"
For Firefox: The page just keeps loading and loading, never stops.
I'm positive this is my Default Gateway. I am not typing it in wrong or in the wrong place.
If you could help, please do. Thanks
